WEBVTT

23:26.830 --> 23:29.040 line:80%
Your parents and uncle
were killed one after another.

23:29.040 --> 23:30.150 line:80%
Although you are the victim,

23:30.150 --> 23:31.220 line:80%
you are also a witness.

23:31.220 --> 23:32.790 line:80%
Until the case is solved,

23:33.040 --> 23:34.440 line:80%
you cannot leave Lin'an.
